code: public int complete(Session session, CommandLine commandLine, List<String> candidates) {     // grab selected camel context from the first argument     String contextName = null.     String[] args = commandLine.getArguments().     if (args != null && args.length > 1) {         // 0 is the command name itself         // 1 is the first argument which is the camel context name         contextName = args[1].     }     try {         StringsCompleter delegate = new StringsCompleter().         List<Map<String, String>> routes = getRoutes(contextName).         for (Map<String, String> row : routes) {             delegate.getStrings().add(row.get("routeId")).         }         return delegate.complete(session, commandLine, candidates).     } catch (Exception e) {     // nothing to do, no completion     }     return 0. }
